{"tid":243711,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"奇怪大學生","createTime":"2017-05-14T23:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T17:56:18.000Z","uid":91404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6c329c87c96b053f42c05caf5d28a2370fdfc10e","tid":243711,"uid":91404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T23:25:14.000Z","msg":"話說我之前兩個人同組做groupmate<br />\n兩個女既，咁present 完之後佢地就約小弟去食個tea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啦，點知惡夢就開始⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n首先我地行的途中佢地兩個分別見到佢地熟人衝左埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而我因爲唔識就禮貌地保持一定距離，等佢地講完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知佢地一路講一路講，之後愣地個熟人話你地係咪有個fd(即係我等緊） 佢地一齊話唔緊要，佢等得，唔洗理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後告別熟人後，佢地好似行路途中<br />\n一個行最前，一個行中間，我就行最後、而唔係正常並排行，十分尷尬<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/072038_ea5c782bd81cfa4dd301fb1a0113faa9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F072038_ea5c782bd81cfa4dd301fb1a0113faa9.jpg&h=c4c93752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最奇怪係我地食野，我同其中一個講<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  野，咁講野當然視線要望住人<br />\n但佢坐我對面唔應我，而係繼續望電話，之後當我尷尬2、3分鐘後收翻個視線後，佢先施施然放低部電話，打完佢個message,回覆翻3分鐘前的說話，好奇"},{"pid":"92a1cd38f21e686a2f5e06ad94fb2e97143181fe","tid":243711,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T23:27:08.000Z","msg":"軍訓差唔多啦"},{"pid":"37d9183a578420ba63619e5e3c40effc9309e4f9","tid":243711,"uid":91404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T23:33:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>軍訓差唔多啦</blockquote><br />\n我係受邀去食既個tea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過程非常後悔，寧願唔去算<br />\n好似將示意圖咁每個人大約有三步距離，都唔知應該點，細路仔未見過大場面"},{"pid":"dfdafb32e58664929d9c12d6f135c8785afd470e","tid":243711,"uid":91404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T23:49:00.000Z","msg":"正常人類溝通社交模式應該唔係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c5391e26451706a2d434a985f6a4a12082f95f","tid":243711,"uid":91404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T00:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c5b97e070130776a88b691089def7b78f116ff","tid":243711,"uid":91404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T03:29:28.000Z","msg":"無人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b414f17ff183f0d8417bbdf3850b9c06d51009","tid":243711,"uid":124312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c329c87c96b053f42c05caf5d28a2370fdfc10e","tid":243711,"uid":91404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T23:25:14.000Z","msg":"話說我之前兩個人同組做groupmate<br />\n兩個女既，咁present 完之後佢地就約小弟去食個tea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啦，點知惡夢就開始⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n首先我地行的途中佢地兩個分別見到佢地熟人衝左埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而我因爲唔識就禮貌地保持一定距離，等佢地講完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知佢地一路講一路講，之後愣地個熟人話你地係咪有個fd(即係我等緊） 佢地一齊話唔緊要，佢等得，唔洗理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後告別熟人後，佢地好似行路途中<br />\n一個行最前，一個行中間，我就行最後、而唔係正常並排行，十分尷尬<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/072038_ea5c782bd81cfa4dd301fb1a0113faa9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F072038_ea5c782bd81cfa4dd301fb1a0113faa9.jpg&h=c4c93752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最奇怪係我地食野，我同其中一個講<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  野，咁講野當然視線要望住人<br />\n但佢坐我對面唔應我，而係繼續望電話，之後當我尷尬2、3分鐘後收翻個視線後，佢先施施然放低部電話，打完佢個message,回覆翻3分鐘前的說話，好奇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T17:56:05.000Z","msg":"巴打 我都係<br />\n最近一位舊同學 唔算好熟<br />\n佢邀請我同佢影畢業相<br />\n我放工就去搵佢<br />\n點知去到就同你遭遇差不多<br />\n佢竟然同幾個fd一齊圍埋唔理我咁 仲傾電話問我等唔等得 <br />\n無幾耐先同我影番張相<br />\n之後佢地有個fd 主動同我傾計 我都同佢傾左一排  但我真正同影相ge 同學又唔係好理我咁<br />\n心諗：其實你唔想理我 就唔好叫我黎"},{"pid":"540562b46926bb40bb6014ab8173aaf5eee78f50","tid":243711,"uid":124312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T17:56:18.000Z","msg":"好奇怪"}]}